This is the first test release of the wxPlot package. 
The original code was taken from the PLplot library 
(http://emma.la.asu.edu/plplot/) and was modified for using it 
with wxWindows. 

This is the list of plplot files and corresponding wxPlot files 
(taken from plplot-990122.tar.gz:

